{"tid":190574,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇中石油（857）","createTime":"2017-04-07T08:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T07:19:53.000Z","uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5c708f8a8e6d6393289c07eb6ebae07fe557d0","tid":190574,"uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"油價近年開始回穩<br />\n而中石油屬於下油產業<br />\n直接受惠油價上升<br />\n而佢依家既現價又好吸引<br />\n大家入唔入？"},{"pid":"411c12e30866492cce6a895fbf2ad545e2a6c620","tid":190574,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"前排入左"},{"pid":"4cad1a9f220965e19140749fabe60af5addc5d54","tid":190574,"uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排入左</blockquote><br />\n咩價位？<br />\n你都睇好中石油？"},{"pid":"c1581c8fcb4dc3931a5fa3033ce59f9bc928f7a3","tid":190574,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:40:25.000Z","msg":"幾時重返10蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59bd7de0b041fb677d8041a275a85bc90121eee","tid":190574,"uid":19421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"14.99既時候入左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩有得減2.5"},{"pid":"874a53de52defadb9b57e7fc25e9911d64f01d3a","tid":190574,"uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時重返10蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有幾多蟹貨？"},{"pid":"5eb87541f6c32944f796ae8a902d45fa357a1f7e","tid":190574,"uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"中國石油（00857）發盈喜，預計今年第一季轉虧為盈，賺50億至60億元(人民幣，下同）。公司去年首季錄得虧損137.86億元。<br />\n中石油說，首季全球石油市場逐步趨向平衡，國際油價按年大幅上升，預計今年餘下的三季，國際油價中低位震盪運行存在較大不確定性。集團將努力保持生產經營平穩向好，提高市場競爭力。<br />\n另外，中石油公布，控股股東中國石油集團計劃以持有的中石油A股發行可換股債券，期限不超過5年，集資金額不超過100億元。今次債券發行仍有待國資委及中國證監會核准"},{"pid":"669c118584bdfc7fcfb94db932ee92bf9b90d403","tid":190574,"uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"盈喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7decfd64cfa68a4af378b766578fde35a1c2a632","tid":190574,"uid":25213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"6蚊入左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2494a38dcc8abe7c3a24df58011a910c1ad38e97","tid":190574,"uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6蚊入左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐到依家？"},{"pid":"9f2384912736b66c2cddf806cf46959b3a26d662","tid":190574,"uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6蚊入左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐到依家？</blockquote><br />\n不過我覺得今年上得返7炆"},{"pid":"b9884ceea35d7ac229c6d7470fb915f8fd0db3d6","tid":190574,"uid":25213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6蚊入左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐到依家？</blockquote><br />\n係，鬥長命"},{"pid":"9a75812b83cbdbc8d9adfdb1d5aed10ffda3f65a","tid":190574,"uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"唉 又跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0648b19cee9d2bdb1163df52e26739a476a1c7","tid":190574,"uid":182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉 又跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係時候入貨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fbe0e7f4fa3e68b21f9570a585f9ef42fba01e","tid